                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-54-victim462 t18151025-54-viclabel312"></join> by trade. I lost my gown and petticoat on the 17th of October; the prisoner came to my bed three times, and would not go away; he slept in the same lodging room that we did. When I got up in the morning, I found my things all gone, and he was gone too.</p>
